        <h1>
            Inflation, Investment Fees, and Savings Goals:
            Three Numbers That Shape Your Future
        </h1>

        <p class="hero-copy article-lead">
            Inflation changes the target, investment fees affect the
            journey, and monthly contributions determine how much of
            the work must come from you.
        </p>

        <p class="card-meta">
            Published July 17, 2026
        </p>
